author: Jason Brennan
title: TV | Live Rugby World Cup 2015 - Argentina vs Australia
text: Argentina take on Australia in this 4.00pm kick-off in Twickenham, with a place in next weekend's final up for grabs. Argentina produced an excellent performance in their quarter-final to overcome Ireland 43-20, while the Wallabies had to work much harder to edge past Scotland 35-34. However, Australia will still go into the match as slight favourites given they have won 18 of the previous 24 meetings between the sides, including a 34-9 win in Mendoza when the sides last met three months ago.Nothing is set in stone though, and if this world cup has shown us anything, it's not what pundits predict is rarely the outcome.
